# Project Overview

This is an inventory management system for O.T.R.A FOOD DISTRIBUTION.

The project is divided into two main parts:
-   **Frontend**: A React (Vite) application located in the `[frontend](mdc:frontend)` directory. It uses Tailwind CSS and Shadcn UI for styling and components.
-   **Backend**: A Node.js and Express application located in the `[backend](mdc:backend)` directory. It uses MongoDB as the database with Mongoose for ODM.

Key technologies include:
- Frontend: React, Vite, Tailwind CSS, Shadcn UI, react-router-dom
- Backend: Node.js, Express, MongoDB, Mongoose, JWT for authentication
